dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Sawtooth Ridge and Emigrant Hill quadrangles, Kern County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Sawtooth Ridge and Emigrant Hill map
Geology Sawtooth Ridge and Emigrant Hill quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.

"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Sawtooth Ridge, CA 1961, Revised 1994, DMA 1955 IINE-Series V895; Emigrant Hill, CA 1953, photorevised 1973, AMS 2055 III NW-Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
